CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 2, 1962, pg. 1, reads: "With Friends - Congressman Scranton is pictured here with Ambrose Lane, Maurice Goldstein, fiery Squirrel Hill legislator, and Dr. Brady O. Hopper. (In background is William Johnson)... - All Photos by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Pennsylvania gubernatorial candidate William "Bill" Scranton with Ambrose Lane, Maurice Goldstein, Dr. Brady O. Hopper, and William Johnson in background, at Republican banquet, Loendi Club
